Title: ANY SIZE & SHAPE Custom Floor access doors
Body (HTML):
Custom Steel Floor Hatches – Tailored to Your Needs  

Our steel floor hatches are fully customizable to ensure a perfect fit and seamless integration into your space. Personalize your hatch with the following options:  

- Precise Dimensions: Designed to match your exact opening size.  
- Hinge Placement: Choose hinges on the short or long side.  
- Flush or Lip Design: Select a flush finish or a 2-inch lip to cover the surrounding surface.  
- Custom Color: Pick a color that complements your style.  
- Weight & Thickness: Specify estimated weight and thickness for tiling or additional coverings.  
- Optional Border: Add an overall border and define the required depth.  

Crafted for durability, functionality, and style, our hatches are ideal for any residential, commercial, or industrial application.

HOW TO PLACE THE ORDER:

  1. Round up your opening dimensions to the nearest odd numbers and pick them from size options in the listing ( that is only for fair pricing and making payment )
  2. Provide your exact specs by filling personalization slot
  3. Place an order

HOW TO PICK THE COLOR:
- You can pick any color from any collection by following this link: neokem.eu/en/color-charts.

ETA ( FLOOR HATCHES )
- Making shop drawing: 3-5 days
- Fabrication: 3 weeks
- Shipping: 5-10 days
